snippet.title: Atari 8-bit - Mickey in the Great Outdoors [Atari] 1983
snippet.description:
Mickey in the Great Outdoors, 
 an educational game by Walt Disney Productions.
Published by Atari (1983).

Recorded with Easycap USB 2.0 from a real Atari 600XL (PAL) + Atari 1064 memory module + Atari "Happy"1050
